00:01:26,640 --> 00:01:30,360
=Dream of Chang'An=

13
00:01:30,360 --> 00:01:33,080
=Episode 49=

14
00:01:34,400 --> 00:01:36,280
I've summoned everyone again

15
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:38,720
because I have something important
to announce.

16
00:01:51,840 --> 00:01:53,280
This is the legendary posthumous edict,

17
00:01:53,720 --> 00:01:55,600
written by the late emperor himself

18
00:01:56,320 --> 00:01:58,160
after the Morning Dew Rebellion.

19
00:02:03,240 --> 00:02:04,240
All these years,

20
00:02:05,240 --> 00:02:07,160
it has been sealed within a painting.

21
00:02:09,080 --> 00:02:09,759
And now,

22
00:02:10,560 --> 00:02:11,800
it has finally seen the light of day again.

23
00:02:20,640 --> 00:02:21,600
This posthumous edict

24
00:02:23,680 --> 00:02:24,680
is the real one.

25
00:02:29,720 --> 00:02:30,600
Your Majesty.

26
00:02:36,880 --> 00:02:37,800
But

27
00:02:38,680 --> 00:02:40,440
there's more to it than meeting the eye.

28
00:02:41,840 --> 00:02:43,120
That is why

29
00:02:44,160 --> 00:02:45,360
I've summoned everyone here.

30
00:02:46,400 --> 00:02:47,640
I need to explain

31
00:02:48,560 --> 00:02:49,880
the secret behind the posthumous edict.

32
00:03:14,970 --> 00:03:16,120
(Thirteenth Uncle, Prince Guang)

33
00:03:16,500 --> 00:03:17,570
(My fifth younger brother, Prince Yi)

34
00:03:19,920 --> 00:03:20,480
This...

35
00:03:21,080 --> 00:03:22,120
What's going on?

36
00:03:23,000 --> 00:03:23,960
How is this possible?

37
00:03:26,040 --> 00:03:26,680
The posthumous edict

38
00:03:27,480 --> 00:03:29,080
was written using special ink.

39
00:03:30,600 --> 00:03:31,600
The ink will never disappear.

40
00:03:32,640 --> 00:03:34,080
Only four words

41
00:03:36,600 --> 00:03:37,920
will disappear
once they touch water.

42
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:04,720
Uncle, you have treated me with
such kindness and virtue.

43
00:04:05,800 --> 00:04:09,200
But the late emperor and I used you.

44
00:04:37,840 --> 00:04:38,440
Your Majesty.

45
00:04:58,600 --> 00:05:00,080
Back then, before the start
of the Morning Dew Rebellion,

46
00:05:00,960 --> 00:05:02,680
the late emperor was afraid
that the plan might fail.

47
00:05:03,800 --> 00:05:05,160
That's why he met me in private.

48
00:05:06,320 --> 00:05:09,680
He wanted me to imitate Goujian.

49
00:05:11,200 --> 00:05:12,760
He wanted me to acknowledge
Qiu Ziliang as my father

50
00:05:15,680 --> 00:05:17,160
and inherit the throne.

51
00:05:20,080 --> 00:05:21,600
Since the late emperor
wanted to protect me,

52
00:05:22,640 --> 00:05:23,880
he had to let another person

53
00:05:25,520 --> 00:05:26,480
be the centre of

54
00:05:26,480 --> 00:05:27,880
Qiu Ziliang's attention and hatred.

55
00:05:30,080 --> 00:05:31,280
That's why

56
00:05:35,440 --> 00:05:37,360
he chose Prince Guang.

57
00:05:42,480 --> 00:05:43,560
So that's the case.

58
00:05:44,520 --> 00:05:46,680
I was wondering why the late emperor

59
00:05:47,680 --> 00:05:49,360
would pass the throne to me

60
00:05:50,560 --> 00:05:52,600
when he didn't even like me.

61
00:05:54,880 --> 00:05:56,960
After the Morning Dew Rebellion failed,

62
00:05:58,560 --> 00:05:59,640
Qiu Ziliang

63
00:06:01,160 --> 00:06:02,480
didn't kill my brother.

64
00:06:04,440 --> 00:06:05,960
Instead, he put him under house arrest.

65
00:06:07,680 --> 00:06:08,680
And Brother

66
00:06:09,880 --> 00:06:12,000
had urged me

67
00:06:12,480 --> 00:06:13,520
to proceed

68
00:06:15,600 --> 00:06:17,600
with the plan.

69
00:06:27,920 --> 00:06:29,120
Uncle,

70
00:06:30,840 --> 00:06:32,480
you were always on a mountain retreat.

71
00:06:33,880 --> 00:06:35,440
That's how you were able
to escape the disaster.

72
00:06:43,800 --> 00:06:46,560
So, were you the one behind it?

73
00:06:47,080 --> 00:06:47,920
Yes.

74
00:06:51,440 --> 00:06:52,120
I

75
00:06:53,760 --> 00:06:55,400
didn't completely agree

76
00:06:55,400 --> 00:06:56,280
with the late emperor's plan.

77
00:06:57,720 --> 00:07:01,920
I wasn't willing to let you suffer
on my behalf.

78
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:09,840
That's why I ordered my men
to spread the news.

79
00:07:10,360 --> 00:07:13,880
I told them to say that you have to
distance yourself from wars and conflict

80
00:07:14,800 --> 00:07:17,760
because you were instructed by a saint
to do so.

81
00:07:20,640 --> 00:07:23,520
Using that to my advantage,
I did live in seclusion.

82
00:07:24,480 --> 00:07:25,600
Qiu Ziliang

83
00:07:25,920 --> 00:07:27,240
did stop hunting for me after that.

84
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:34,480
So, we saved each other.

85
00:07:36,960 --> 00:07:37,800
Indeed.

86
00:07:46,800 --> 00:07:48,400
If I were blinded by greed

87
00:07:48,680 --> 00:07:51,400
and inherited the throne
using the posthumous edict,

88
00:07:52,960 --> 00:07:54,520
I'm afraid I would be
the laughing stock of the world

89
00:07:56,960 --> 00:07:57,960
once

90
00:07:58,480 --> 00:08:00,600
the truth has been revealed.

91
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:08,360
Uncle, that won't happen.

92
00:08:10,200 --> 00:08:11,720
People often say that
humans are unpredictable.

93
00:08:12,800 --> 00:08:13,960
But Uncle,

94
00:08:15,640 --> 00:08:17,520
you only became who you are

95
00:08:19,560 --> 00:08:20,880
by overcoming such ordeals.

96
00:08:49,680 --> 00:08:50,680
Today,

97
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:54,280
I summoned all of you here

98
00:08:56,000 --> 00:08:59,480
to witness this ceremony.

99
00:09:01,160 --> 00:09:02,040
I

100
00:09:05,640 --> 00:09:09,600
will select Prince Guang
as the Crown Prince.

101
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:14,920
Your Majesty.

102
00:09:27,840 --> 00:09:28,800
Uncle,

103
00:09:30,480 --> 00:09:32,440
you deserved everything.

104
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:48,040
I will humbly accept your edict.

105
00:09:49,440 --> 00:09:51,000
Thank you, Your Majesty.

106
00:09:56,080 --> 00:10:01,280
Long live Your Majesty.

107
00:10:26,160 --> 00:10:26,880
Your Majesty,

108
00:10:29,880 --> 00:10:31,200
the new generals of the Shencai Army

109
00:10:31,320 --> 00:10:32,360
have assumed command.

110
00:10:33,000 --> 00:10:34,040
Before this, Li Zening

111
00:10:34,200 --> 00:10:35,880
was bewitched by Left Minister's
Peach Blossom Jade Bangle

112
00:10:36,000 --> 00:10:37,000
and committed a grave mistake.

113
00:10:37,400 --> 00:10:38,280
Official Li wrote a letter personally

114
00:10:38,280 --> 00:10:39,640
to beg leniency for her sake.

115
00:10:42,040 --> 00:10:43,080
Your Majesty, please take a look.

116
00:10:44,960 --> 00:10:46,040
I understand.

117
00:10:46,400 --> 00:10:47,440
You may leave.

118
00:10:48,760 --> 00:10:49,280
Yes, Your Majesty.

119
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:02,760
Your Majesty,

120
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:04,320
I thought Han Ding...

121
00:11:08,440 --> 00:11:09,360
Speak.

122
00:11:10,240 --> 00:11:11,920
Wasn't Han Ding a traitor?

123
00:11:12,800 --> 00:11:14,280
The Left Minister tried to bribe him.

124
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:17,080
I told him to outwit them
with their tricks.

125
00:11:20,920 --> 00:11:21,840
So,

126
00:11:22,680 --> 00:11:23,480
Your Majesty,

127
00:11:23,480 --> 00:11:25,040
when you wrote
a retirement letter for Uncle Huaizhi

128
00:11:25,400 --> 00:11:26,640
and sent me away,

129
00:11:27,160 --> 00:11:29,000
were all of those part of your plan?

130
00:11:33,680 --> 00:11:34,320
I

131
00:11:37,240 --> 00:11:39,000
was just afraid that
I would die suddenly

132
00:11:39,800 --> 00:11:41,040
like my brother.

133
00:11:42,120 --> 00:11:43,360
If that happens,

134
00:11:43,920 --> 00:11:44,640
I

135
00:11:45,680 --> 00:11:46,680
don't want you

136
00:11:46,680 --> 00:11:47,960
to stay by my side

137
00:11:50,040 --> 00:11:51,320
and laugh at me.

138
00:11:52,280 --> 00:11:53,200
Nonsense.

139
00:11:53,600 --> 00:11:54,760
You mustn't curse yourself,

140
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:55,520
understood?

141
00:11:58,320 --> 00:11:59,720
The sons of the Qi Family,

142
00:12:01,800 --> 00:12:05,040
it's either they are too young,
or they are mediocre.

143
00:12:06,520 --> 00:12:07,920
After much thought,

144
00:12:08,920 --> 00:12:10,160
I figured out that Uncle

145
00:12:11,320 --> 00:12:12,840
was the only one
who could accomplish this task.

146
00:12:15,600 --> 00:12:16,480
And

147
00:12:17,680 --> 00:12:19,520
he stood up to my test.

148
00:12:21,200 --> 00:12:22,000
That's why

149
00:12:23,960 --> 00:12:25,560
I came up with that idea.

150
00:12:28,040 --> 00:12:28,800
That's not it.

151
00:12:29,480 --> 00:12:30,560
Actually,

152
00:12:31,240 --> 00:12:32,920
I had that idea in my mind long ago.

153
00:12:34,720 --> 00:12:35,960
I just didn't dare to think about it.

154
00:12:36,920 --> 00:12:38,280
I didn't dare to hope.

155
00:12:40,720 --> 00:12:41,600
But now,

156
00:12:48,360 --> 00:12:50,040
I finally have the chance to do so.

157
00:12:51,720 --> 00:12:53,320
Your Majesty, you mean...

158
00:13:09,120 --> 00:13:09,840
Yu'er,

159
00:13:14,440 --> 00:13:16,280
we can finally be together.

160
00:13:20,960 --> 00:13:22,160
I wish to spend the rest of my life

161
00:13:23,600 --> 00:13:24,920
with you.

162
00:13:48,840 --> 00:13:50,040
You have suffered so much

163
00:13:50,040 --> 00:13:50,960
because of me.

164
00:13:52,640 --> 00:13:53,280
I

165
00:13:55,600 --> 00:13:56,840
will remember
what you did for me forever.

166
00:13:59,600 --> 00:14:00,600
Now,

167
00:14:02,560 --> 00:14:03,240
we can

168
00:14:03,240 --> 00:14:04,560
finally be together.

169
00:14:05,600 --> 00:14:07,680
We can lead the lives we want.

170
00:14:36,100 --> 00:14:37,300
(Yijia Gambling Den)

171
00:14:58,380 --> 00:15:00,540
(Zuiyue Wine Store)

172
00:15:31,440 --> 00:15:32,680
