175
00:15:38,920 --> 00:15:39,680
It's the Lantern Festival.

176
00:15:54,080 --> 00:15:54,600
Your Majesty,

177
00:15:54,880 --> 00:15:55,720
let me borrow her for a moment.

178
00:16:11,960 --> 00:16:13,400
(Yan's Textile)
Where are you bringing me?

179
00:16:18,960 --> 00:16:19,640
What's wrong?

180
00:16:21,440 --> 00:16:23,040
His Majesty summoned me during the day.

181
00:16:23,280 --> 00:16:25,000
He thanked me for my assistance.

182
00:16:25,520 --> 00:16:26,720
He asked me about my requests.

183
00:16:27,360 --> 00:16:28,600
So, what are your requests?

184
00:16:32,040 --> 00:16:33,360
My requests?

185
00:16:35,080 --> 00:16:35,600
First,

186
00:16:36,040 --> 00:16:37,240
I want a panacea

187
00:16:38,680 --> 00:16:39,840
so that my looks can be restored.

188
00:16:41,240 --> 00:16:42,040
Second,

189
00:16:42,240 --> 00:16:44,600
I wish to travel around the Four Seas,

190
00:16:46,120 --> 00:16:47,120
and have ample food and clothing.

191
00:16:49,640 --> 00:16:50,680
Third,

192
00:16:51,840 --> 00:16:52,720
I wish for a husband.

193
00:16:53,480 --> 00:16:54,040
No.

194
00:16:54,160 --> 00:16:55,080
You can't take His Majesty away from me.

195
00:17:00,120 --> 00:17:01,720
No one wants your emperor.

196
00:17:08,440 --> 00:17:09,319
Third,

197
00:17:09,520 --> 00:17:10,839
I wish for a husband,

198
00:17:11,160 --> 00:17:12,760
a strong and healthy husband.

199
00:17:14,920 --> 00:17:16,280
Look at His Majesty.

200
00:17:16,680 --> 00:17:18,200
In just one year,

201
00:17:18,560 --> 00:17:20,359
from a strong warrior,

202
00:17:20,480 --> 00:17:22,040
he ended up in that state.

203
00:17:27,440 --> 00:17:29,040
Only a silly girl like you

204
00:17:29,160 --> 00:17:30,120
cares about him.

205
00:17:37,280 --> 00:17:38,240
Since young,

206
00:17:40,120 --> 00:17:41,520
I have always admired the prosperous
state of the Xing empire.

207
00:17:52,080 --> 00:17:54,000
(Zuiyue Wine Store)

208
00:17:58,440 --> 00:18:01,000
I've seen the dances and singing
during times of peace.

209
00:18:03,320 --> 00:18:04,640
I've seen

210
00:18:07,680 --> 00:18:08,680
the flames of war as well.

211
00:18:09,600 --> 00:18:10,600
Although it's a pity

212
00:18:11,320 --> 00:18:13,080
that I wasn't able to witness
a peaceful world,

213
00:18:14,080 --> 00:18:16,920
I know that countless loyal officials

214
00:18:17,560 --> 00:18:19,600
and brave warriors had
sacrificed their lives

215
00:18:20,320 --> 00:18:23,680
to produce such a splendid scene.

216
00:18:26,760 --> 00:18:27,600
I have

217
00:18:29,760 --> 00:18:30,960
no regret in life now.

218
00:18:35,560 --> 00:18:36,200
Yu'er,

219
00:18:38,800 --> 00:18:39,560
thank you.

220
00:18:47,480 --> 00:18:48,160
Yu'er,

221
00:18:50,520 --> 00:18:51,880
I'll return home tomorrow.

222
00:19:05,640 --> 00:19:06,400
Take care.

223
00:19:07,800 --> 00:19:08,520
Take care.

224
00:19:12,990 --> 00:19:15,850
(Yan's Textile)

225
00:20:05,120 --> 00:20:05,640
Your Majesty,

226
00:20:05,920 --> 00:20:07,080
the jujube cake I bought just now

227
00:20:07,080 --> 00:20:07,880
was delicious.

228
00:20:08,040 --> 00:20:08,640
There's

229
00:20:08,640 --> 00:20:09,400
an osmanthus cake stall in the front.

230
00:20:09,400 --> 00:20:10,160
Their cakes are delicious as well.

231
00:20:11,600 --> 00:20:13,240
You should eat more then.

232
00:20:13,400 --> 00:20:14,320
Let us buy more of them.

233
00:20:15,080 --> 00:20:16,000
Even if they're delicious,

234
00:20:16,000 --> 00:20:17,280
we can't buy too many of them.

235
00:20:17,560 --> 00:20:18,960
We can visit this place

236
00:20:18,960 --> 00:20:20,080
during next year's Lantern Festival.

237
00:20:21,200 --> 00:20:21,640
By the way,

238
00:20:21,880 --> 00:20:25,200
I think Han Ding has his hands full.

239
00:20:25,600 --> 00:20:27,000
I've trained him for a long time.

240
00:20:27,120 --> 00:20:28,800
This is the time for him
to prove his usefulness to me.

241
00:20:29,520 --> 00:20:30,920
Just let him hold them.

242
00:20:31,560 --> 00:20:32,120
I

243
00:20:32,720 --> 00:20:34,160
wish to see the results of his training.

244
00:20:34,920 --> 00:20:35,960
I thought you loved the cakes?

245
00:20:36,400 --> 00:20:37,120
Although I do love them,

246
00:20:37,120 --> 00:20:38,720
I can't consume them any more.

247
00:20:39,640 --> 00:20:40,240
We can

248
00:20:40,240 --> 00:20:41,680
enjoy them

249
00:20:41,760 --> 00:20:42,640
on the next Lantern Festival.

250
00:20:45,100 --> 00:20:47,270
♪You don't realize the deep feelings♪

251
00:20:47,280 --> 00:20:47,920
Your Majesty,

252
00:20:48,200 --> 00:20:49,200
what's wrong?

253
00:20:50,340 --> 00:20:52,520
♪The voice was low and close yesterday♪

254
00:20:53,160 --> 00:20:56,420
♪It's hard for an isolated force
to hide the light rhythm♪

255
00:20:56,920 --> 00:20:58,040
I was just thinking

256
00:20:58,920 --> 00:21:00,440
that for the next Lantern Festival,

257
00:21:04,440 --> 00:21:05,440
I'm afraid

258
00:21:06,000 --> 00:21:08,810
♪Love and hate drag down those
who aren't involved♪

259
00:21:09,720 --> 00:21:11,560
I will have no time to accompany you.

260
00:21:12,840 --> 00:21:15,050
♪Is my heart♪

261
00:21:18,600 --> 00:21:20,120
But Yu'er, promise me this.

262
00:21:21,320 --> 00:21:22,680
Even if you're on your own,

263
00:21:24,720 --> 00:21:26,360
you need to travel happily

264
00:21:27,760 --> 00:21:29,040
and enjoy the delicacies.

265
00:21:29,270 --> 00:21:31,070
♪Protecting the warm winter♪

266
00:21:31,580 --> 00:21:34,270
♪Enjoying life with that longing♪

267
00:21:35,100 --> 00:21:37,150
♪The golden dagger-axe
releases the sunny sky♪

268
00:21:37,660 --> 00:21:40,750
♪Enjoying half a day of escape♪

269
00:21:40,800 --> 00:21:41,440
All right?

270
00:21:42,520 --> 00:21:43,160
Your Majesty,

271
00:21:43,520 --> 00:21:44,000
did you forget?

272
00:21:44,200 --> 00:21:45,720
I'm the best at both of these.

273
00:21:45,800 --> 00:21:46,880
I promise you.

274
00:21:47,760 --> 00:21:48,320
Even if I were

275
00:21:48,320 --> 00:21:49,680
to visit this place by myself next time,

276
00:21:49,840 --> 00:21:50,760
I would surely

277
00:21:50,840 --> 00:21:52,560
share all of the delicacies with you,

278
00:21:52,840 --> 00:21:53,440
all right?

279
00:21:53,440 --> 00:21:54,970
♪The voice was low and close yesterday♪

280
00:21:55,880 --> 00:21:58,700
♪It's hard for an isolated force
to hide the light rhythm♪

281
00:21:59,350 --> 00:22:01,790
♪Why is fate secretly torturing me?♪

282
00:22:02,460 --> 00:22:04,670
♪One must learn to have compassion
on women♪

283
00:22:05,050 --> 00:22:07,550
♪There are too many trivial times
in this world♪

